# pii-patterns.local.txt — operator-private PII patterns for the parity tests.
# Copy this file to pii-patterns.local.txt (gitignored) and list one regex per
# line: your machine names, brand names, personal names, private IP prefixes.
# Lines starting with '#' are comments. Each pattern is asserted NOT to appear
# in any deployed windows script (InstallerParity) or default brand rule
# (UserPromptExtract).
(?i)your-machine-name
your-private-brand
